Package com.github.cyberryan1.cybercore.spigot.command.helpers

Class CommandSettings

java.lang.Object
com.github.cyberryan1.cybercore.spigot.command.helpers.CommandSettings
Direct Known Subclasses:
BaseCommand
public class CommandSettings
extends java.lang.Object
Contains all the settings for a command. Contains constructors, getters, setters, and checkers (but no chess (please laugh)) for the settings.
Author:
CyberRyan1
